N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 141.3 - Identification of IDV- and DV-eligible cases

State Regulations

Procedures shall be established in each
court so as to insure that cases pending before it are identified as
IDV-eligible or DV-eligible at the earliest possible time. Notes
